name: Quipt Home Medical Corp.
longDescription: Quipt Home Medical Corp provides in-home monitoring equipment, supplies, and services to patients. The company's services consist of Daily & Ambulatory Aides, Power Mobility, INR Self-Testing, Respiratory Equipment Rental, Home ventilation, Oxygen Therapy, and Sleep Apnea & PAP Treatment.
